        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "briefDescription": "The scheme \"Training for Horticulture Skill Development for Self-Employment at Centre of Excellence \" is aimed at promoting self-employment opportunities across all communities in Gujarat through practical and theoretical learning at the Centre of Excellence.\n\n",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme &amp;quot;Training for Horticulture Skill Development for Self-Employment at Centre of Excellence&amp;quot; introduced by the Agriculture, Farmers Welfare and Cooperation Department, Gujarat,  aims to offer structured training programs ranging from 10 to 30 days, focusing on horticultural skills to enable self-employment. The program is tailored for individuals across all social categories, with subsidized training costs. Beneficiaries gain access to a complete learning experience, including expert sessions, training literature, educational tours, and practical kits.\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- **Stipend:** ₹250/- per trainee.- **Other Facilities:** Dining facility, training literature kit, experiential education tour, trainee kit, etc.\n> **Duration of the Training:**\n\n\n- Minimum: 10 days\n- Maximum: 30 days\n\n",
        "exclusions_md": "",
